  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To specify the long term evolution of Nephronophthisis in terms of renal disease as well as
      extra-renal damages for patients having a confirmed diagnosis of NPHP1, NPHP2, NPHP3, NPHP4,
      NPHP5, NPHP6 or NPHP8 gene mutation
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
